name: jabber-caps-browser
tagline: Explore features advertised by Jabber clients
body: jabber-caps-browser is an addon to [jabber.el](http://emacs-jabber.sourceforge.net/), the Emacs Jabber client.  It offers a visual presentation of the features supported by the Jabber clients that your contacts use.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
